* Residue topology file for TIP4P and quantum water, for FlucQ
* 
    18 1
MASS     4 HP     1.00800 ! TIP4P WATER HYDROGEN
MASS     5 MP     0.0     ! TIP4P WATER M-SITE
MASS    58 OP    15.99940 ! TIP4P WATER OXYGEN
MASS    11 HTQ    1.00800
MASS    81 OWQ   15.99940

RESI TIP4 .000   ! TIP4P WATER MODEL
GROUP
ATOM OH2  OP      0.00
ATOM H1   HP      0.52
ATOM H2   HP      0.52
ATOM M1   MP     -1.04
BOND OH2  H1    OH2  H2    H1 H2    M1 H1  M1 H2  ! Bonds between M site and hydrogens are needed for FlucQ
THET H1   OH2  H2
PATC  FIRS NONE LAST NONE

RESI QWAT    .000
GROUP
 ATOM OH2Q  OWQ     0.000  ! Let the charge be zero so no need to adjust
 ATOM H1Q   HTQ     0.000  ! NONB lists for eletrostatics
 ATOM H2Q   HTQ     0.000
PATC  FIRS NONE LAST NONE
BOND OH2Q H1Q  OH2Q H2Q  H1Q H2Q  ! This bonds are needed to avoid vdW terms on this atoms!!
END
